# 1. Force SQL Detection
# This ensures GitHub counts your database work in the language bar
*.sql linguist-detectable=true
*.sql linguist-language=SQL

# 2. Ignore Data and Documentation
# This prevents large data files or extra docs from skewing percentages
data/* linguist-vendored
00_database_infrastructure/*.md linguist-documentation
scripts/README.md linguist-documentation

# 3. Standardize Line Endings
# Keeps the code consistent between Windows and Linux/GitHub
* text=auto
*.py text eol=lf
*.sql text eol=lf